ata-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_14907825\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_14907825\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 25, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104oiu1745977288707.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oiu1745977288707.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oiu1745977288707.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"oiu1745977288707\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">UX widgets (field, entity, and component) can specify <code class=\"ph codeph\">IncludeScript</code> for\n\t\ttheir script and declarations containers in the physical definition of the\n\t\twidget.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oiu1745977288707__section_w167ab1b5b1_w168ab1b5_w169ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\">The properties that can be added to the physical definitions of UX widgets are\n\t\t\t\tfollowing:</p>\n<div class=\"sectiondiv\">\n<p class=\"p\">[Field UX widget]</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104oiu1745977288707_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"oiu1745977288707__codeblock_cfm_hrd_2fc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">{declarations = INCLIB:DECL_FLD_WIDGET} \n{script = INCLIB:SCRIPT_FLD_WIDGET}\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">DECL_FLD_WIDGET</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">SCRIPT_FLD_WIDGET</code> contain\n\t\t\t\t\tthe code fragments defined in the <code class=\"ph codeph\">IncludeScript</code> library\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">INCLIB</code>, which is included in the declarations and script\n\t\t\t\t\tcontainers, respectively, for the field object bound to this widget.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sectiondiv\">\n<p class=\"p\">[Entity UX widget]</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104oiu1745977288707_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"oiu1745977288707__codeblock_kxy_hsd_2fc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">{declarations = INCLIB:DECL_ENT_WIDGET} \n{collection_script = INCLIB:SCRIPT_COLL_WIDGET}\n{occurrence_script = INCLIB:SCRIPT_OCC_WIDGET}\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">DECL_ENT_WIDGET</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">SCRIPT_COLL_WIDGET</code>, and\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">SCRIPT_OCC_WIDGET</code> contain the code fragments defined in the\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">IncludeScript</code> library <code class=\"ph codeph\">INCLIB</code>, which is\n\t\t\t\t\tincluded in the declarations, collection script, and occurrence script\n\t\t\t\t\tcontainers, respectively, for the entity object bound to this widget.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sectiondiv\">\n<p class=\"p\">[Component UX widget]</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104oiu1745977288707_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"oiu1745977288707__codeblock_oyv_b2b_vhc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">{declarations = INCLIB:DECL_COMP_WIDGET}\n{component_script = INCLIB:SCRIPT_COMP_WIDGET}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">DECL_COMP_WIDGET</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">SCRIPT_COMP_WIDGET</code> contain\n\t\t\t\t\tthe code fragments defined in the <code class=\"ph codeph\">IncludeScript</code> library\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">INCLIB</code>, which is included in the declarations and component\n\t\t\t\t\tscript containers, respectively, for the component bound to this widget.</p>\n</div>\n<p class=\"p\">In case of an invalid <code class=\"ph codeph\">IncludeScript</code> reference that does not exist,\n\t\t\t\tthe compiler generates a compilation error. The following examples show errors for\n\t\t\t\tinvalid references across all widget types:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"oiu1745977288707__table_wwv_t3b_vhc\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"oiu1745977288707__table_wwv_t3b_vhc__entry__1\">Widget Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"oiu1745977288707__table_wwv_t3b_vhc__entry__2\">Invalid Reference</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"oiu1745977288707__table_wwv_t3b_vhc__entry__3\">Compilation Error</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"oiu1745977288707__table_wwv_t3b_vhc__entry__1\">Field</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"oiu1745977288707__table_wwv_t3b_vhc__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">INCLIB:INVALID_SCRIPT_FLD_WIDGET</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"oiu1745977288707__table_wwv_t3b_vhc__entry__3\"><samp class=\"ph msgph\">1000 - Cannot find include script 'INCLIB:INVALID_SCRIPT_FLD_WIDGET' for widget\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t'customFieldWidget' in the widget definition configuration\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tfiles.</samp></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"oiu1745977288707__table_wwv_t3b_vhc__entry__1\">Entity</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"oiu1745977288707__table_wwv_t3b_vhc__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">INCLIB:INVALID_SCRIPT_ENT_WIDGET</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"oiu1745977288707__table_wwv_t3b_vhc__entry__3\"><samp class=\"ph msgph\">1000 - Cannot find include script 'INCLIB:INVALID_SCRIPT_ENT_WIDGET' for widget\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t'customEntityWidget' in the widget definition configuration\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tfiles.</samp></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"oiu1745977288707__table_wwv_t3b_vhc__entry__1\">Component</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"oiu1745977288707__table_wwv_t3b_vhc__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">INCLIB:INVALID_SCRIPT_COMP_WIDGET</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"oiu1745977288707__table_wwv_t3b_vhc__entry__3\"><samp class=\"ph msgph\">1000 - Cannot find include script 'INCLIB:INVALID_SCRIPT_COMP_WIDGET' for\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\twidget 'customComponentWidget' in the widget definition\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tconfiguration files.</samp></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"oiu1745977288707__note_mdy_ljw_c3c\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Invalid <code class=\"ph codeph\">declaration</code> references behave the\n\t\t\t\tsame way as invalid <code class=\"ph codeph\">IncludeScript</code> references. The following example\n\t\t\t\tshows the equivalent error for a <code class=\"ph codeph\">declaration</code>.</div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"oiu1745977288707__table_nnb_wkw_c3c\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"oiu1745977288707__table_nnb_wkw_c3c__entry__1\">Widget Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"oiu1745977288707__table_nnb_wkw_c3c__entry__2\">Invalid Reference</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"oiu1745977288707__table_nnb_wkw_c3c__entry__3\">Compilation Error</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"oiu1745977288707__table_nnb_wkw_c3c__entry__1\">Any</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"oiu1745977288707__table_nnb_wkw_c3c__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">declarations:INVALID_DECL_REF</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"oiu1745977288707__table_nnb_wkw_c3c__entry__3\"><samp class=\"ph msgph\">1000 - Cannot find include script\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t'declarations:INVALID_DECL_REF' for widget '&lt;widget-name&gt;' in\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthe widget definition configuration files.</samp></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qyo1701663851047.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>[PhysicalWidgetName]</a><p>This section, as defined in the web.ini file, defines a single physical UX web widget for Dynamic Server Page (DSP) components, including the name of the widget class that implements the client (browser) side of the widget, the JavaScript, Module, and CSS URLs that are required to run the widget class, some placeholder layout HTML used by the IDE and IDE property definitions.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/scc1665702919621.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Compiler Messages</a><p>Understand the error, warning, or information messages that might display for the compiler.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_14907825\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_14907825\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "How to define a UX Widget IncludeScript Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 25, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 UX widgets (field, entity, and component) can specify IncludeScript for their script and declarations containers in the physical definition of the widget. The properties that can be added to the physical definitions of UX widgets are following: [Field UX widget] Explain this code {declarations = INCLIB:DECL_FLD_WIDGET} {script = INCLIB:SCRIPT_FLD_WIDGET} Copy DECL_FLD_WIDGET and SCRIPT_FLD_WIDGET contain the code fragments defined in the IncludeScript library INCLIB , which is included in the declarations and script containers, respectively, for the field object bound to this widget. [Entity UX widget] Explain this code {declarations = INCLIB:DECL_ENT_WIDGET} {collection_script = INCLIB:SCRIPT_COLL_WIDGET} {occurrence_script = INCLIB:SCRIPT_OCC_WIDGET} Copy DECL_ENT_WIDGET , SCRIPT_COLL_WIDGET , and SCRIPT_OCC_WIDGET contain the code fragments defined in the IncludeScript library INCLIB , which is included in the declarations, collection script, and occurrence script containers, respectively, for the entity object bound to this widget. [Component UX widget] Explain this code {declarations = INCLIB:DECL_COMP_WIDGET} {component_script = INCLIB:SCRIPT_COMP_WIDGET} Copy DECL_COMP_WIDGET and SCRIPT_COMP_WIDGET contain the code fragments defined in the IncludeScript library INCLIB , which is included in the declarations and component script containers, respectively, for the component bound to this widget. In case of an invalid IncludeScript reference that does not exist, the compiler generates a compilation error. The following examples show errors for invalid references across all widget types: Widget Type Invalid Reference Compilation Error Field INCLIB:INVALID_SCRIPT_FLD_WIDGET 1000 - Cannot find include script 'INCLIB:INVALID_SCRIPT_FLD_WIDGET' for widget 'customFieldWidget' in the widget definition configuration files. Entity INCLIB:INVALID_SCRIPT_ENT_WIDGET 1000 - Cannot find include script 'INCLIB:INVALID_SCRIPT_ENT_WIDGET' for widget 'customEntityWidget' in the widget definition configuration files. Component INCLIB:INVALID_SCRIPT_COMP_WIDGET 1000 - Cannot find include script 'INCLIB:INVALID_SCRIPT_COMP_WIDGET' for widget 'customComponentWidget' in the widget definition configuration files. Note: Invalid declaration references behave the same way as invalid IncludeScript references. The following example shows the equivalent error for a declaration . Widget Type Invalid Reference Compilation Error Any declarations:INVALID_DECL_REF 1000 - Cannot find include script 'declarations:INVALID_DECL_REF' for widget '<widget-name>' in the widget definition configuration files. Related Links [PhysicalWidgetName] This section, as defined in the web.ini file, defines a single physical UX web widget for Dynamic Server Page (DSP) components, including the name of the widget class that implements the client (browser) side of the widget, the JavaScript, Module, and CSS URLs that are required to run the widget class, some placeholder layout HTML used by the IDE and IDE property definitions. Compiler Messages Understand the error, warning, or information messages that might display for the compiler. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}